A. Download the Neabot APP and register an account;
B. Follow the prompts of the Neabot APP to configure the network of the Neabot sweeper;
C. Add Neabot SKILL and log in to the account and password registered in the first step;
D. Wait for Alexa to update the device list, then customize a name for the device, and the configuration is complete.

Supported Devices: Neabot vacuum.
Supported Actions: turn on, turn off.

Here are some of the phrases you can use for voice commands to control your vacuum. 
Alexa, turn on Neabot
Alexa, turn off Neabot

Note: "Neabot" is sample custom robot name. If you've named your Neabot vacuum, you can use its name to control it through Alexa.
